Hypothermia Prevention Shelter January 15 & 16, 2026  
  
Living Savior Lutheran Church will again partner with Bethlehem Lutheran Church to provide meals to guests staying at Bethlehem, 8922 Little River Turnpike, Fairfax, VA 22031. Living Savior will be responsible for providing breakfast, lunch and dinner on January 16. Breakfast and lunch should be dropped off at Bethlehem between 5:30-7:30pm on January 15th. Dinner should be brought to Bethlehem and served on January 16th by 5:30 pm. Please consider volunteering to make a breakfast casserole, provide lunch items, or make and serve dinner at Bethlehem.


MENU:
- **Breakfast**: Casserole, Juice, Fruit
- **Brown Bag Lunch**: Sandwich, Cookie, Chips & Drink
- **Dinner**: Lasagna, Bread Roll, Salad, and Drink


Sign up to volunteer through the Signup Genius [HERE](https://www.signupgenius.com/go/4090A4BABA62DA3F58-61437292-hypothermia)
